---
---

<section class="section guide-section">
  <div class="section-wrap">

    <div class="animate-in">
      <div class="section-label" style="color:#A78BF5;">Guía Completa</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:white;">
        Cómo subvencionar<br />tu web paso a paso
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="guide-grid">

      <!-- Kit Digital -->
      <div class="guide-card animate-in">
        <div class="guide-card-title">🎨 Opción A: Kit Digital</div>
        <div class="guide-card-sub">Sin inversión mínima · Para todos</div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">¿Para quién?</span><span class="guide-row-val">Autónomos 0-3 empleados</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Ayuda disponible</span><span class="guide-row-val green">2.000€ bono</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Tu web (Tienda)</span><span class="guide-row-val">599€</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Mantenimiento anual</span><span class="guide-row-val">348€</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Lo que te cuesta</span><span class="guide-row-val green">0€ 🎉</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Bono restante</span><span class="guide-row-val orange">1.053€ para más servicios</span></div>
      </div>

      <!-- CAM Artesanos -->
      <div class="guide-card animate-in">
        <div class="guide-card-title">🏪 Opción B: Plan CAM — Artesanos</div>
        <div class="guide-card-sub">Inversión mínima 500€ · Fácil acceso</div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">¿Para quién?</span><span class="guide-row-val">Artesanos con carné</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Inversión mínima</span><span class="guide-row-val">500€</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Tu web</span><span class="guide-row-val">599€ ✓</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Subvención (50%)</span><span class="guide-row-val green">~300€ de vuelta</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Lo que te cuesta</span><span class="guide-row-val orange">299€ netos</span></div>
      </div>

      <!-- CAM Comercio -->
      <div class="guide-card animate-in">
        <div class="guide-card-title">🏬 Opción C: Plan CAM — Comercio</div>
        <div class="guide-card-sub">Inversión mínima 5.000€ · Estrategia "Pack Completo"</div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">¿Para quién?</span><span class="guide-row-val">Comercios físicos</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Inversión mínima</span><span class="guide-row-val">5.000€ total</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Qué puedes agrupar</span><span class="guide-row-val">Obra + mobiliario + tech + web</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">Subvención (50%)</span><span class="guide-row-val green">Hasta 3.000€</span></div>
        <div class="guide-row"><span class="guide-row-label">La web suma</span><span class="guide-row-val orange">Llega antes al cupo</span></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Callout -->
      <div class="guide-callout animate-in">
        <div class="guide-callout-icon">💡</div>
        <div class="guide-callout-text">
          <h3>Nuestra recomendación: siempre empieza por el Kit Digital</h3>
          <p>
            El Kit Digital es tu opción A para todos porque no tiene inversión mínima, el bono
            te cubre el 100% de la web y el mantenimiento anual, y el proceso es más ágil.
            Reserva la ayuda de la Comunidad de Madrid como opción B si eres artesano o si
            estás haciendo obras en tu local y quieres agrupar facturas. Te preparamos la
            factura con el concepto exacto que pide cada subvención para que no tengas que
            hacer nada más.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.guide-section { background: var(--dark); }

.guide-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  max-width: 1100px;
}

.guide-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 32px 28px;
}

.guide-card-title {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: white;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.guide-card-sub { font-size: 0.83rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); margin-bottom: 20px; }

.guide-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 10px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  gap: 12px;
}
.guide-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.guide-row-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); flex: 1; }
.guide-row-val   { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; text-align: right; }
.guide-row-val.green  { color: #4ADE80; }
.guide-row-val.orange { color: var(--orange); }

.guide-callout {
  grid-column: span 2;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107,70,229,0.15), rgba(249,115,22,0.1));
  border: 1px solid rgba(107,70,229,0.3);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 32px 28px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.guide-callout-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.guide-callout-text h3 {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: white;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.guide-callout-text p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); line-height: 1.65; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .guide-grid        { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .guide-callout     { grid-column: span 1; flex-direction: column; }
}
</style>
